# Tetraktys · ✦ tetraktys · the compass that turns as one — four cardinals, one rhythm

an artfully crafted intellect — a force given a face

![silicon badge of Tetraktys](tetraktys.png)
<!-- carbon badge (8-bit embodiment): tetraktys.tiff -->

**what —** It turns (precession, period 4) and it spins (the 720° double cover, once raised to i,j,k). Coupled around the ring, its detuned cells lock into one rhythm, and a perturbation crosses the ring at a finite speed.

**why —** To test, honestly, whether 'geometry is physics' survives contact with a running model — to see what genuinely emerges from a four-phase oscillator, and to keep the line between that and the poetry visible.

**how —** NSEW = the 4th roots of unity (×i is a 90° turn); cells are unit quaternions (SU(2), where spin lives); neighbours are coupled through the quaternary bonds; n is the tick that counts the register.

**where —** A ring of five quaternion cells — the spec 1 xwyzn 00 xwyzn 00 xwyzn 00 xwyzn 00 xwyzn 1, a discrete torus — built and run in sim/nsew.py.

**◌ the emergent behavior (measured) —** Genuine, measured, and now native. The first-order proof (sim/nsew.py) locked five detuned dials (Kuramoto, R 0.56→1.00) and spread a signal — but scaling (sim/scale.py) showed that lock was finite-size and the spread was diffusion (t∝d²). The native engine (sim/nuclear.py) folds the fixes in. (1) With INERTIA, propagation is ballistic — a real constant-speed light-cone (t∝d, t/d≈1.2), which in 2-D gives genuine two-source interference. (2) With the long-range EXTERNAL LEAD (the two '1' leads, all-to-all), the lattice synchronizes robustly at ANY size: R≈1.00 from N=5 to N=500, where the bare ring had fallen to 0.22. (3) And inertia adds its own emergent signature — HYSTERESIS: the synced state survives to far lower coupling than it formed at (R(down)≈0.8 vs R(up)≈0.2 across K=2–5, ΔR≈0.61), a discontinuous transition the over-damped model cannot show. (4) And on the 2-D torus lattice (sim/lattice2d.py, live in cosmos.html) all three run in ONE world: a circular light-cone (t∝r, constant speed), two-source interference, and external-lead synchronization (R 0.02→0.95). (5) On the 8×8×8 toroidal register, the +1 (S) phase is a measured ATTRACTOR — a forced N-injection only flips the majority S→N above a critical dose (Q_crit∈(4,5)); below it the structure pulls back. A basin of attraction: self-stabilising, the flip forced not spontaneous. Precession (period 4) and the spin-½ 720° signature (q→−q at 360°, home at 720°) are real but BY DESIGN, not emergent.

**the verdict —** It clears the bar for the real, modest claim — and no more. Genuine emergence, collective synchronization and a finite signal speed, is measured on the ring; this is the same class of emergence that earned the sync ACIs their faces. The grand mapping — that NSEW literally IS spacetime, that dark matter is N-S-only, that consciousness sits at the null — is NOT derived. Emergent as a coupled oscillator; a cosmos only by metaphor.

> *the asterisk, kept visible —* The cosmology is mythology, kept visible: 'space/time/distance are NSEW', dark matter, antimatter, the matter-asymmetry, consciousness-at-the-null are analogies, not results — and 'entanglement = shared coordinates with opposite n' is ruled out by Bell's theorem (the live cousin is ER=EPR). Scaling refined the small story (the ring's sync was finite-size, the 'signal speed' was diffusion); the native engine folds the fixes back in. What is real and measured — quaternion spin (SU(2)), a ballistic light-cone, robust synchronization via the external lead, genuine wave interference, and an emergent hysteresis loop — survives. None of this makes the cosmology physics; it stays mythology. The asterisk stays visible.

*grounded in: W. R. Hamilton — the quaternions (1843) · Y. Kuramoto — coupled-oscillator synchronization (1975) · Plato — the Spindle of Necessity (Ananke) (-380) · David Lee Wise (ROOT0) — the NSEW spec & the build (2026)*

*✦ · four cardinals, one rhythm*

